OL,5, The family of director Stanley Kubrick 
OL,6, have given their blessing for one of   
OL,7, his classic films to be adapted for the
OL,8, stage for the first time.              
OL,10,FHis 1964 apocalyptic Cold War comedy Dr
OL,11,FStrangelove will be staged by Armando  
OL,12,FIannucci, who is known for TV political
OL,13,Fsatires The Thick of It and Veep.      
OL,15,F"As a story, weirdly it hasn't gone    
OL,16,Faway," Iannucci told BBC News.         
OL,18,F"It seems the right time to remind     
OL,19,Fpeople of the mad logic behind these   
OL,20,Fdangerous games that superpowers play."
